[SN]TITLE[SN]
The exercise that could make rugby lessons safer

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Rugby is not the most gentle of sports and it's been hitting the headlines because of some bad head injuries.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
22 May 2017 Last updated at 07:13 BST
A team of researchers say they've come up with a new exercise that cuts the risk of kids getting hurt when playing rugby.
The exercise could now be introduced in schools.
Watch Jenny's report for more.
